# Group: accessories
msgid "OP_group_accessories"
msgstr "附加工具"

# Option: show attachment helper
msgid "OP_showAttachmentHelper"
msgstr "疊加卡助手"

# Tooltip: show attachment helper
msgid "OP_showAttachmentHelper_tooltip"
msgstr ""
"提供卡牌大小的袋子用於容納疊加於其它卡上的卡牌\n"
"（例如：背包）。"

# Option: show CYOA campaign guides
msgid "OP_showCYOA"
msgstr "「選擇你自己的冒險」戰役指南"

# Tooltip: show CYOA campaign guides
msgid "OP_showCYOA_tooltip"
msgstr ""
"展示於重新設計的、採用“選擇你自己的冒險”\n"
"風格的戰役指南中。"

# Option: show displacement tool
msgid "OP_showDisplacementTool"
msgstr "位移工具"

# Tooltip: show displacement tool
msgid "OP_showDisplacementTool_tooltip"
msgstr ""
"可將主遊戲區域內的物品\n"
"統一移動至選定方向。 "

# Option: show hand helper
msgid "OP_showHandHelper"
msgstr "手牌統計助手"

# Tooltip: show hand helper
msgid "OP_showHandHelper_tooltip"
msgstr ""
"你再也不用自己數手牌數了！這項工具會替你完成，\n"
"甚至還可以計算你的手牌上限。"

# Option: show search assistant
msgid "OP_showSearchAssistant"
msgstr "查找助理"

# Tooltip: show search assistant
msgid "OP_showSearchAssistant_tooltip"
msgstr ""
"快速地從你的牌堆頂部查找\n"
"3，6，9或是X張牌！"

# Option: Token Arranger settings
